      <p style="font-size: 16px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 12px;"><strong style="color: var(--text);">Rupert Murdoch:</strong> Called Trump's behavior "a huge disservice to the country. Pretty much a crime." Told a Fox executive: "We want to make Trump a non person."</p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 12px;"><strong style="color: var(--text);">The settlement: $787.5 million</strong> — the largest known media defamation settlement in U.S. history. A separate Smartmatic lawsuit seeking $2.7 billion remains ongoing.</p>
