      title="Nevada and Wisconsin"
      body="<strong>Nevada:</strong> 6 fake electors indicted for offering false instruments for filing and uttering forged instruments. Case proceeding after Nevada Supreme Court ruled 6-0 it could continue.<br><br><strong>Wisconsin:</strong> 3 defendants (including Chesebro) charged with felony forgery. In December 2025, a judge ruled sufficient evidence existed to send the case to trial."
